               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500708-name-198" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-198" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-198" type="surname" value="LOVELOCK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-198" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LOVELOCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Vauxhall-road. On Saturday night, before I went before the Magistrate, about twenty minutes before ten o'clock, I was sitting near my own house—I saw the prisoners going in a direction from Vauxhall-bridge towards Pimlico—I then saw them come back—I saw them go near Mr. Thompson's shop, and Hill picked up this caddy from the board outside, and put it under his coat—he then walked up and down the road—I told a policeman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500708-name-199" type="witnessName">
