                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, B</hi> 199). Lovelock spoke to me—I went to White-street, and saw the two prisoners together—Hill said, "Here comes the policeman—I took Hough, with this caddy on his arm—he said, "I did not steal it"</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
