                  </hi>. This is my caddy; it was safe on a table at my door about an hour before it was taken.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Hill's Defence.</hi> I was going to Chelsea, and the policeman took me; I had nothing to do with the caddy.</p>
